1.1.0.name: wordpress/wpjaipho
1.1.0.description:
WPJaipho is plugin which adds mobile optimized look & feel to your WP based galleries. It is based on the original Jaipho, iPhone optimized Javascript gallery and it works on iPhone, iPad and Android devices.

Supported WP galleries

WP Jaipho works with: NextGEN Gallery and Default WP Gallery (via Media Library). It also works flawlessly with some mobile theme plugins such as WPTouch and WordPress Mobile Pack.

How Does it Work?

Simple enough - just activate the plugin, and all your galleries are automatically transformed into mobile optimized gallery, which is visible for mobile users only. Check out demo here with your iPhone.
